DESCRIPTION:<a href="https://tfl.gov.uk/tube-dlr-overground/status/?Input=&lineIds=&dateTypeSelect=Future%20date&direction=&startDate=2026-04-03T03:30:00&endDate=2026-04-04T00:29:00">Disruption map.</a>\n\nLIONESS LINE: Good Friday\, 3 April\, no service between Willesden Junction and Watford Junction. There will also be no BAKERLOO LINE service between Stonebridge Park and Watford Junction\, no LONDON NORTHWESTERN RAILWAY services between Euston and Milton Keynes Central\, and no SOUTHERN services between Shepherds Bush and Watford Junction. Special bus service 718 operates between Stonebridge Park and Harrow & Wealdstone via Wembley High Road (Park Lane)\, Wembley Central\, North Wembley\, Preston Road (for Metropolitan line and bus route 223 to/from South Kenton) and Kenton. Special bus service 720 operates between Harrow-on-the-Hill (for Metropolitan line) and Watford Junction via Harrow & Wealdstone\, Headstone Lane\, Hatch End (Harrow Arts Centre)\, Carpenders Park (Prestwick Road)\, Bushey (Eastbury Road) and Watford High Street.
